{"tid":822424,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"決定以後只會自己去旅行","createTime":"2018-09-16T10:27:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T11:06:35.000Z","uid":172024,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fd6f7ea987744926e3acf0041b1ed320a74f4021","tid":822424,"uid":172024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:27:25.000Z","msg":"旅行真係會見真章 <br />\n同熟既朋友去 以為有默契 <br />\n去完關係仲衰過唔去之前 <br />\n以後都係獨L自己一個去旅行算9數<br />\n雖然影相係麻煩啲 <br />\n但寧願叫陌生人幫自己影<br />\n雖然未必影到想要既效果 <br />\n但最少 我會感激佢肯幫自己影 <br />\n就算唔滿意都唔緊要 <br />\n帶住開心既心情繼續旅行<br />\n仲有最怕同人去旅行又無得罪佢 <br />\n黑口黑面 佢自己唔開心就算 <br />\n最慘係影響埋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人同我一樣 <br />\n寧願自己一個去旅行  <br />\n咩都唔洗煩 鐘意去邊就去邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔使睇人面色！！"},{"pid":"8d080c14d0c850422a8e976fdf50da6c4bf9041b","tid":822424,"uid":178332,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:30:54.000Z","msg":"自己去梗係正好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38f43887288dc4cb2b35d367aad59463a8467363","tid":822424,"uid":23758,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:32:07.000Z","msg":"得一個人<br />\n對住幾靚既風景都冇用<br />\n冇人係隔離分享一樣既心情<br />\n然後一個人會好撚悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bfaaedecac4e033ad08af41da24c5abdfa7ac80","tid":822424,"uid":103226,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:34:13.000Z","msg":"一個人先叫真正旅行同放鬆<br />\n同人去你某程度上係應酬緊"},{"pid":"1f1efd91b7376b834ee2b41d6e963e4ec0f46d59","tid":822424,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:43:37.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"df36a54668dc6d4d4299a0c89ec89c49f8713eb6","tid":822424,"uid":196459,"like":0,